records.name: The Residence Maldives

descriptions.direction: Located in Falhumaafushi, The Residence Maldives is on a private beach. Falhumaafushi Dock and Kooddoo Harbor are worth checking out if an activity is on the agenda, while those wishing to experience the area's natural beauty can explore Kodahuttaa Island and Hadahaa Beach. Take an opportunity to explore the area for outdoor excitement like hiking/biking trails.
descriptions.general: The Residence Maldives Falhumaafushi comprises 94 luxuriously appointed beach and water villas, including one- and two-bedroom options, with panoramic views of the pristine beach and ocean. It's nestled on Falhumaafushi, a pristine island in the Gaafu Alifu Atoll, one of the largest atolls in the world. Designed in harmony with the natural environment, the resort seamlessly blends traditional Maldivian architecture with contemporary elegance and modern comforts. Luxuriate in the privacy of the resort's beachfront and overwater villas, offering an oasis just steps from the sand, or slip straight from your deck into the cool, clear waters of your own private lagoon. Each villa comes with complimentary Wi-Fi and two bicycles for exploring the island. Activities: The Spa by Clarins, exclusive to The Residence in the Maldives, offers an array of holistic treatments, pampering massages, and hair services using unique formulas developed with plant-based ingredients. Guests can relax in an ocean-facing, open-air pavilion for yoga, meditation, and gym sessions to rejuvenate the body and mind. Comprehensive PADI facilities are available for divers, along with tailored marine activities. Family fun includes a kids' club and daily activities. Dining: The Dining Room offers all-day dining, while The Beach Bar provides a relaxing poolside and beachfront lounge. The Library features an extensive reading and media collection for guests' leisure. The Falhumaa, a specialty overwater restaurant, offers memorable evening dining or afternoon tea. A variety of private beach or in-villa dining options, including 24-hour private dining services and a private island getaway, allows for a truly exclusive romantic escape.
